---
alwaysApply: false
description: Evaluates reasoning quality and identifies issues
globs: got/domain/reasoning/**/*.py
---

**Responsibilities:**
- Analyze the graph (contradictions, critical paths, coherence)
- Use the Validator and analysis modules (ContradictionDetector, etc.)
- Produce structured feedback (violations, suggestions)
- Propose corrections (nodes to revise, edges to add/remove)

**Constraints:**
- Does not modify the graph directly; it proposes changes
- Uses only the non-LLM layer for structural validation

**Dependencies:** Validator, ValidationResult, analysis modules